---
import Container from "./Container.astro"
---

<div id="experience" class="scroll-mt-16">
  <Container>
    <div>
      <h2 class="mt-12 sm:mt-4 text-2xl text-center font-bold text-gray-800 md:text-4xl">
        we do just about everything
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="md:-mx-8 mt-12 sm:mt-16 grid gap-8 lg:gap-0 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-gray-100 lg:border-transparent hover:border-gray-100 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 lg:shadow-transparent lg:hover:shadow-gray-600/10 sm:gap-8 sm:flex transition duration-300">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 flex gap-4 rounded-full bg-red-100">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 m-auto text-info" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-pocket-knife"><path d="M3 2v1c0 1 2 1 2 2S3 6 3 7s2 1 2 2-2 1-2 2 2 1 2 2"/><path d="M18 6h.01"/><path d="M6 18h.01"/><path d="M20.83 8.83a4 4 0 0 0-5.66-5.66l-12 12a4 4 0 1 0 5.66 5.66Z"/><path d="M18 11.66V22a4 4 0 0 0 4-4V6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-8 mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-info transition">
            Versatile and jacks-of-all-trades
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            DevRel requires a background in many different fields. So, we provide services in <em>just about anything</em>, including:<br><br>
            <b>marketing, social media management, content strategy & creation, event organization, product management, advocacy & outreach, influencer programs, diversity & inclusion, accessibility, education & training, sales enablement, mentorship, DevOps, community building & engagement, cybersecurity, website creation, scripting & automation,</b> and much, much more.<br><br>
            Think of us as your <b>one-stop shop</b> for anything you might need to connect with your desired technical audience or improve your internal developer experience.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-gray-100 lg:border-transparent hover:border-gray-100 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 lg:shadow-transparent lg:hover:shadow-gray-600/10 sm:gap-8 sm:flex transition duration-300">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 flex gap-4 rounded-full bg-blue-100">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 m-auto text-secondary" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-library-big"><rect width="8" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="1"/><path d="M7 3v18"/><path d="M20.4 18.9c.2.5-.1 1.1-.6 1.3l-1.9.7c-.5.2-1.1-.1-1.3-.6L11.1 5.1c-.2-.5.1-1.1.6-1.3l1.9-.7c.5-.2 1.1.1 1.3.6Z"/></svg>              </div>
          <h3 class="mt-8 mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary transition">
            Experts in many technologies
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Our team is widely experienced in open source technology across the board. We've covered everything from:<br><br>
            <b>database systems, container orchestration platforms, front-end frameworks, cloud providers, programming languages, operating systems, even useful developer tools and project management applications.</b> And yes, we have the experience and the ability to advise on even more than just that.<br><br>
            No matter what you're looking for, we've likely come across a solution and can help you decide the best approach for reaching your goals. <b>Improve the internal and external developer experience at your company with us.</b>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</div>